name: Confinement 21-Proceed 2
description:
This video is a version of the video-performance that in a few days will be presented as part of the Encierro 21 program, within the International Biennial of Contemporary Art of the South (BIENALSUR). Video-performance that directly visualizes social and psychological suffering that many are suffering in these times of pandemic and confinement.

Edition 1/1
1920-1980

Performance: Frank Lahera O´Callaghan
Creation: Frank Lahera O´Callaghan
Original music: Rafael Borges Hernández (ART PANKE STUDIOS)
